import React, { Fragment } from 'react'
import {
    Header,
    Title,
    Description,
    RepoContainer,
    Icons,
    StarNumber

} from './styles'

import { BiStar } from "react-icons/bi"

const Card = (props) => {
    return (
        <Fragment>
            <Header>{props.number} repositórios</Header>
                <RepoContainer>
                <Title>{props.title}</Title>
                <Description>{props.description}</Description>
                <Icons>
                    <BiStar size={15} /> <StarNumber>{props.star}</StarNumber>
                </Icons>
            </RepoContainer>
        </Fragment>


    )
}

export default Card
